            <div type="translation" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>Lucius Fufius Secundus, veteran of Legion Prima Italica, aged 60</p>
         </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <head>Commentary</head>
                <p>The Legio I Italica has no connection with Kyrenaika; 
                    either Fufius was a native Kyrenaian who had returned 
                    home after service or he belonged to the 3,000 veterans sent to the Kyrenaika 
                    by Trajan after the Jewish revolt of 115-117 C.E.; 
                    this contingent must have been drawn from several legions, 
                    and may have included men from the Danubian legio I Italica</p>
            </div>
